{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0002", "text": "由我去決定誰 才應該在我心中 擁有位置", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 4, 4, 2, 0, 0, 3, 2, 5, 3, 3, 9, 5, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jau4", "ngo5", "heoi3", "kyut3", "ding6", "seoi4", "coi4", "goi1", "zoi6", "ngo5", "sam1", "zung1", "jung2", "jau5", "wai6", "zi3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "由", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "決定", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "應該", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在我心中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "擁有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "位置", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0003", "text": "當你下次 要玩伴時 手機按到沒電時", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 4, 9, 2, 0, 9, 3, 4, 4, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "haa6", "ci3", "jiu3", "waan2", "bun6", "si4", "sau2", "gei1", "on3", "dou3", "mut6", "din6", "si4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "當", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "下次", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "玩伴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "手機", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "按到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒電時", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0004", "text": "情願你別來 找這失勢女子", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 2, 0, 9, 5, 3, 4, 5, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cing4", "jyun6", "nei5", "bit6", "loi4", "zaau2", "ze5", "sat1", "sai3", "neoi5", "zi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "情願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "找", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "失勢", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "女子", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0005", "text": "想起當時 蠢到沒法子 純情得可以", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 9, 0, 9, 4, 2, 4, 9, 0, 0, 3, 9, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["soeng2", "hei2", "si4", "ceon2", "dou3", "mut6", "faat3", "zi2", "seon4", "cing4", "dak1", "ho2", "ji5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "想起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "當時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蠢到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒法子", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "純情", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "可以", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0006", "text": "男生中只得你 贈我戒指", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 3, 9, 3, 5, 2, 5, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["naam4", "sang1", "zung1", "zi2", "dak1", "nei5", "zang6", "ngo5", "gaai3", "zi2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "男生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "贈", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "戒指", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0007", "text": "原來就算最愛我 不過暫時", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 4, 4, 5, 3, 4, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyun4", "loi4", "zau6", "syun3", "zeoi3", "oi3", "ngo5", "bat1", "gwo3", "zaam6", "si4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "原來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "就算", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暫時", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
