{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0009", "text": "一變四 四變十二 來到這禮拜 更加諷刺", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 4, 4, 4, 4, 2, 2, 0, 4, 5, 5, 4, 3, 4, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jat1", "bin3", "sei3", "sei3", "bin3", "sap6", "ji6", "loi4", "dou3", "ze5", "lai5", "baai3", "gaa1", "fung3", "ci3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "一變", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "四", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "四變", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "十二", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "來到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "禮拜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更加", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "諷刺", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0010", "text": "何以 我變了你的 16號愛人", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 5, 5, 4, 5, 5, 3, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ho4", "ji5", "ngo5", "bin3", "liu5", "nei5", "dik1", "oi3", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "何以", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我變", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "16", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "號", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0011", "text": "隨便 碰上哪個她 都比我更有趣吸引", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 4, 5, 4, 3, 3, 9, 5, 5, 4, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ceoi4", "bin6", "pung3", "naa5", "go3", "taa1", "dou1", "bei2", "ngo5", "jau5", "ceoi3", "kap1", "jan5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "隨便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "碰上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哪個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "她", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "都", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "更", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有趣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吸引", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0012", "text": "偶爾我亦 願我是別人", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 5, 2, 2, 5, 2, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngau5", "ji5", "ngo5", "jik6", "jyun6", "ngo5", "si6", "bit6", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "偶爾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "亦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0013", "text": "能轉個化身 共你再蜜運", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 4, 4, 3, 2, 5, 4, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nang4", "zyun2", "go3", "faa3", "san1", "gung6", "nei5", "zoi3", "mat6", "wan6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "化身", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "共", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "再", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "蜜運", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0014", "text": "我以前是冠軍 怎會慣 做後備愛人", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 0, 2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 2, 2, 2, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "ji5", "cin4", "si6", "gun1", "gwan1", "zam2", "gwaan3", "zou6", "hau6", "bei6", "oi3", "jan4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "以前", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "冠軍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎會慣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "後備", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛人", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0015", "text": "曾經 也上到最高 逐漸滑落 谷底的暗", "structure": {"line_index": 15, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 3, 5, 4, 4, 3, 2, 2, 2, 2, 3, 9, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cang4", "ging1", "jaa5", "dou3", "zeoi3", "gou1", "zuk6", "zim6", "waat6", "lok6", "guk1", "dai2", "dik1", "am3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "曾經", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最高", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "逐漸", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "滑落", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "谷底", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暗", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "16號愛人", "artists": ["容祖兒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_753", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0014", "next_line_id": "lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzUz_0016", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
